```go
type io.Reader interface {
    Read(p []byte) (n int, err error)
}
```
The fundamental reading interface. Read reads up to len(p) bytes into p. Returns the number of bytes read (0 <= n <= len(p)) and any error. Returns io.EOF when stream ends.

```go
type io.Writer interface {
    Write(p []byte) (n int, err error)
}
```
The fundamental writing interface. Write writes len(p) bytes from p. Returns the number of bytes written and any error. Must return a non-nil error if n < len(p).

